Web generalization uses the Mind2Web dataset (Deng et al., 2023;
https://osu-nlp-group.github.io/Mind2Web/) and is graded with the
answer-blind Online-Mind2Web protocol (arXiv:2504.01382). Mind2Web task
data under `evaluation_examples/examples/mind2web/` is redistributed for
research use; please cite the original authors.

Model serving uses vLLM (https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm) and the
Qwen3.5 / MiniMax-M3 model families.
